      "title": "OUTCOME 1: Addressing Needs",
      "short_name": "Services and supports are accessible and responsive",
      "legend_label": "Addressing needs",
      "description": "High-quality, timely, flexible, and coordinated services are delivered in a manner that is respectful of and builds on the strengths of the individual, family, and the community to reduce reliance on intensive supports in the long-term.",
