          "name": "Report and respond to child safety concerns",
          "supporting": [
            {
              "name": "Report concerns about child abuse or neglect",
              "desc": "Anyone who suspects a child is being abused or neglected is legally required to report it. The 24/7 hotline connects you to trained intake workers.",
